\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Like the woman said, Papi\u8217\'92s dead. He don\u8217\'92t want em.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 Mandri could feel the rest of the Ayramun glaring at him.}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93I don\u8217\'92t know,\u8221\'94 said Mandri, \u8220\'93It seems a bit rude.\u8221\'94}
\par\plain {\f0\fs24\b0\i0\cf1 \loch\af0\hich\af0\dbch\af0\uc1\u8220\'93Ain\u8217\'92t it, though?\u8221\'94 said a voice in the shadows behind. It was the same gruff man from earlier, named Weeg. Weeg was so dirty and disheveled that he looked like he\u8217\'92d just got done rolling down a dune. His face was unreasonably flat. His nose must have been broken a hundred times.}
